author: A. Pawlowski
title: Pink eye may be a rare symptom
description: What are coronavirus symptoms? Fever and respiratory problems are the most common. Some people may experience redness in the eyes.
content:
The new coronavirus can spread through the eyes, prompting the worlds largest association of eye doctors to urge its members to be aware of the warning signs in patients.
